    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I hear you on the short term, but it feels like the \"business side\" arguments always focus on the struggle to survive, while the \"pro-wage\" side just sounds like idealistic theory that doesn't account for how hard it is to run a real business. Is there actual evidence that these wage hikes don't just end up hurting the very people they're supposed to help?",
